{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Guarantee 100% Pension Transfer to Surviving Spouses",
        "additional_details": "This petition is not just about money\u2014it\u2019s about dignity, fairness, and the recognition of lifelong partnerships. When a person dies, their spouse should not be left to struggle financially. They should be supported by the pension their partner worked hard to earn.\r\nWe call on Parliament to act swiftly and decisively to ensure that surviving spouses receive 100% of their loved one\u2019s pension. Let us build a system that honours the contributions of the deceased and protects the living.\r\n",
        "background": "We call upon the Government to enact legislation that guarantees surviving spouses receive 100% of their deceased partner\u2019s pension\u2014whether state, occupational, or private\u2014without any reduction, delay, or discretionary limitations.",
